$3.99.\n\nTake flowers anywhere, whether you're at home or travelling. A peaceful, calming experience awaits, offering relaxation and creativity. You can live your dream to be a florist or simply enjoy a touch of colorful nature right at your fingertips.\n\nAs you create beautiful floral arrangements, test your knowledge with quizzes on flower names. Challenge yourself to identify the different species and learn more about each flower as you interact with them. This unique feature adds a fun and educational element to the experience, combining creativity with learning.", "short_description": "Immerse yourself in floral beauty with over 30 photorealistic flowers and decorations. Create stunning floral arrangements and test your knowledge with quizzes on flower names. Take flowers anywhere for just $3.99"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "MFR_Landscape_Chinese (0-00-00-00).png", "id": "1796229904247164", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86652081_1796229910913830_201525561031322008_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=IC62mVE7lDoQ7kNvgGa0yPX&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCd21-uumCPSqkRDuzpi2qo0IPfUha5wg15swoWr_OFPQ&oe=6767F547"}, {"file_name": "MFR_Square_Chinese (0-00-00-00).png", "id": "1443130233310385", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974439_1443130236643718_2340786945912971711_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lZ1kEFzjJiIQ7kNvgER1xqv&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCLSu4k7KXsUVFTGwxvkICbMNzoYM_0AwR_kEOb9h7zFQ&oe=6767E378"}, {"file_name": "MFR_Portrait_Chinese (0-00-00-00).png", "id": "1441119926600942", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982535_1441119929934275_5607624163269387893_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Cv2BBywfn1sQ7kNvgE3M9Nr&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.ocul